WEBVTT

01:36.400 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:39.680 --> 01:44.280
BEIYU

01:49.960 --> 01:52.200
CHE YANQIN

02:08.759 --> 02:10.000
The rain in Beiyu keeps falling.

02:11.440 --> 02:13.000
When will it stop?

02:16.520 --> 02:18.680
CHE YANQIN

02:23.000 --> 02:24.320
Let's go watch a movie.

02:33.840 --> 02:35.720
Don't you study today?

02:36.840 --> 02:39.880
I don't want you to look back and remember
every time you came to Beiyu to see me,

02:39.960 --> 02:41.200
all we did was read books.

02:41.800 --> 02:43.160
We should take a break when we need to.

02:49.880 --> 02:50.920
How about this one?

02:53.040 --> 02:54.640
You like horror movies?

02:55.760 --> 02:56.760
I just picked it randomly.

02:58.640 --> 02:59.720
- Is that okay?
- Sure!

03:00.920 --> 03:03.640
Hello. I want two tickets
for Waking Up to Ghosts.

03:04.640 --> 03:05.600
Since then,

03:07.400 --> 03:09.160
I've never gone back to school.

03:10.400 --> 03:12.000
I didn't even step outside.

03:13.080 --> 03:13.920
No one understands me,

03:15.360 --> 03:16.720
except for you.

03:17.240 --> 03:19.200
And no one ever talks to me.

03:28.000 --> 03:29.920
Why are you crying again?

03:30.960 --> 03:32.720
Don't you think
that you can forget a lot of things

03:34.040 --> 03:35.560
when watching horror movies?

03:35.640 --> 03:37.280
Can't other movies make you do that?

03:38.080 --> 03:39.720
It seems horror movies
are better for that.

03:44.240 --> 03:46.480
Are you feeling down?

03:47.440 --> 03:48.280
Are you scared?

03:50.040 --> 03:50.880
No.

03:52.400 --> 03:53.600
It's just about a kid.

03:58.200 --> 04:00.440
Do you want popcorn?

04:03.800 --> 04:04.720
Or water?

04:37.160 --> 04:39.360
3,100 DAYS

05:09.080 --> 05:10.560
What are you doing? What are you doing?

05:11.080 --> 05:12.040
Let go!

05:12.120 --> 05:13.120
- Let go of me!
- Call the police!

05:14.400 --> 05:15.680
Let me go!

05:16.960 --> 05:18.200
Let go of me!

05:18.280 --> 05:19.480
What's your story?

05:20.360 --> 05:21.920
I was the one who helped her.

05:22.440 --> 05:23.400
I know.

05:23.480 --> 05:26.160
I mean, what are you doing
on the street dressed like this?

05:26.240 --> 05:28.920
The drama club of my university
is going to perform The Zoo Story,

05:29.000 --> 05:30.200
by Edward Albee.

05:30.280 --> 05:31.960
I'll play a homeless man in it.

05:32.040 --> 05:35.040
So, I wanted to experience the real life
of a homeless man personally.

05:35.120 --> 05:38.400
Experience it personally?
Are you living too comfortably?

05:39.400 --> 05:41.320
Officer, you don't understand.

05:41.400 --> 05:44.040
Experiencing it personally
is very important for an actor.

05:48.560 --> 05:50.360
Hello! Yifan,

05:50.440 --> 05:52.880
where is the college student who did
a heroic act that you told me about?

05:56.480 --> 05:58.280
You really are my lucky star.

05:58.360 --> 06:00.440
Hi. I'm a reporter
from the First News team

06:00.520 --> 06:02.040
of Urban Channel, Nanwu TV Station.

06:02.120 --> 06:03.480
Can I have an interview with you?

06:04.080 --> 06:06.000
- Sure.
- Thank you!

06:06.720 --> 06:07.720
Shall we go outside?

06:08.360 --> 06:09.320
- Okay.
- Okay.

06:10.280 --> 06:11.160
I'm going out.

06:15.880 --> 06:18.160
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

06:19.040 --> 06:20.480
By the way, how about that street guy?

06:20.560 --> 06:22.480
He is currently placed
in a shelter in the city.

06:22.560 --> 06:25.040
Meanwhile, we are also trying
to contact his family.

06:25.120 --> 06:27.080
He has some mental health issues

06:27.160 --> 06:29.280
because of too much pressure from life.

06:31.400 --> 06:32.880
Shall we start now?

06:33.920 --> 06:36.320
- Could you briefly introduce yourself?
- Sure.

06:36.840 --> 06:39.160
My name is Mu Chengyun.
I am a senior college student.

06:39.240 --> 06:40.920
I was experiencing
the life of a homeless man

06:41.000 --> 06:42.440
as an actor on the street today.

06:43.120 --> 06:45.080
But unexpectedly, a homeless man appeared,

06:45.160 --> 06:46.040
standing there completely naked.

06:46.640 --> 06:47.920
And there was that girl.

06:48.880 --> 06:50.080
She was standing there too.

06:50.160 --> 06:51.440
I was afraid
something dangerous might happen.

06:52.040 --> 06:53.400
You did a heroic act.

06:53.480 --> 06:55.440
So, what did you think after doing it?

07:06.320 --> 07:08.400
PERSON CONCERNED

07:19.320 --> 07:20.280
Is there something on my face?

07:22.280 --> 07:24.840
- No.
- But you were staring at me.

07:28.160 --> 07:30.040
I thought you looked a bit familiar.

07:35.400 --> 07:36.680
The notebook and pen.

07:45.040 --> 07:46.080
Thank you for liking me.

07:47.160 --> 07:49.440
I haven't acted for a long time.
I didn't expect anyone to remember me.

07:50.520 --> 07:51.360
Thank you for your autograph.

07:52.320 --> 07:53.200
I'm leaving now.

08:01.680 --> 08:04.520
MU CHENGYUN

08:10.800 --> 08:11.840
Thanks for your hard work, Yifan.

08:12.360 --> 08:14.200
It's nothing. You've worked hard, Tian.

08:14.280 --> 08:15.240
It's okay.

08:15.320 --> 08:16.880
Tian, Yifan,

08:16.960 --> 08:19.600
- I'll put the equipment in the car first.
- Be careful.

08:20.840 --> 08:21.720
By the way, Yifan,

08:21.800 --> 08:23.280
do you still want someone
to share a rental?

08:23.360 --> 08:25.120
I heard you mention before
that your current roommate

08:25.200 --> 08:26.240
would only rent it for three months.

08:27.280 --> 08:28.720
How long until it expires?

08:28.800 --> 08:30.800
I have a friend who is looking
for someone to share a rental house.

08:30.880 --> 08:32.120
She's a really nice girl.

08:32.200 --> 08:33.640
I think you two could rent
a house together.

08:34.559 --> 08:36.240
- Does she need it urgently?
- No.

08:36.320 --> 08:37.600
She is currently living
at her parents' house.

08:37.679 --> 08:39.360
She can wait
until your roommate moves out.

08:39.440 --> 08:40.960
Just give her a definite answer.

08:42.440 --> 08:43.960
- I'll ask him when I'm home.
- Okay.

08:45.360 --> 08:46.360
I need to answer a call, Tian.

08:46.440 --> 08:48.240
- All right, I'll head out first then.
- Okay.

08:49.120 --> 08:51.080
- Hello?
- Where are you?

08:51.160 --> 08:52.760
Around the neighborhood. What's up?

08:52.840 --> 08:54.760
Come to the supermarket
outside the neighborhood

08:54.840 --> 08:55.880
to buy some things.

08:55.960 --> 08:57.400
Hurry. I can't carry them all.

09:34.200 --> 09:35.760
I'm at the gate of the supermarket now.

09:45.680 --> 09:47.480
MU CHENGYUN

09:48.360 --> 09:49.680
Mu Chengyun…

09:50.400 --> 09:52.040
Why is this name so familiar?

10:03.800 --> 10:06.200
MU CHENGYUN, ACTOR

10:08.680 --> 10:09.800
You like this type?

10:13.360 --> 10:14.840
- Didn't you say you were buying something?
- Let's go.

10:15.440 --> 10:17.960
- You haven't bought them yet?
- We are about to.

10:19.200 --> 10:21.520
So, it's not that you can't carry them now
but won't be able to carry them later.

10:21.600 --> 10:22.640
That's right.

10:34.080 --> 10:35.800
- What's wrong?
- Why are you using another cart?

10:36.480 --> 10:37.800
I have things to buy too.

10:41.360 --> 10:42.640
Don't worry.

10:42.720 --> 10:45.240
I'll still help you carry your things
if you can't carry them later.

10:50.880 --> 10:53.200
How's the home improvement
of your house going?

10:54.520 --> 10:55.480
Why?

10:56.000 --> 10:57.960
I want to talk about it with you.

10:58.880 --> 10:59.880
About what?

11:00.960 --> 11:02.080
When are you moving out?

11:05.360 --> 11:06.280
Do you want to kick me out?

11:09.720 --> 11:10.720
Let's talk about it when the time comes.

11:11.560 --> 11:12.400
I'm not rushing you.

11:12.480 --> 11:15.360
My colleague introduced a girl to me.

11:15.440 --> 11:16.560
She doesn't need it urgently though.

11:16.640 --> 11:18.840
But we need to confirm the timing first.

11:21.560 --> 11:24.160
Okay. I'll check
on the home improvement progress

11:24.240 --> 11:25.160
and let you know then.

11:40.120 --> 11:41.640
Excuse me. Do you need a cart?

11:42.160 --> 11:43.680
- Yes.
- I don't need it anymore. You can take it.

11:43.760 --> 11:44.600
- Okay.
- Thank you.

11:44.680 --> 11:45.520
Thank you.

11:57.920 --> 11:58.840
What are you doing?

12:00.080 --> 12:01.440
I'm calculating the price.

12:02.440 --> 12:04.080
- Where's your cart?
- What price?

12:05.440 --> 12:06.480
The price of the toilet paper.

12:08.320 --> 12:10.120
They're all four-ply.

12:13.200 --> 12:16.600
Twenty-three yuan…
One hundred and twenty grams times 12…

12:18.240 --> 12:21.560
Twenty yuan…
One hundred and forty grams times 15…

12:22.880 --> 12:23.720
Two yuan per roll.

12:24.600 --> 12:26.200
Twenty-three divided by ten…

12:26.760 --> 12:28.920
- Twenty-three divided by…
- One point nine yuan…

12:29.000 --> 12:30.040
or so.

12:30.680 --> 12:33.160
- Then, I'll take this.
- Sure. It's cheaper.

12:36.000 --> 12:37.800
But it only weighs 120 grams.

12:37.880 --> 12:38.920
Then, take the one with ten rolls.

12:41.600 --> 12:42.680
I'll calculate again.

12:44.160 --> 12:45.400
Wen Yifan,

12:45.480 --> 12:47.080
did you come to the supermarket
for a college entrance exam?

12:47.600 --> 12:50.000
The calculation could take you half a year
with your poor math skills.

12:52.560 --> 12:54.680
It's getting late.
I'm afraid you'll turn in a blank paper.

12:54.760 --> 12:55.600
I haven't finished the calculation yet.

12:56.200 --> 12:58.080
I'll do the test for you
this time, all right?

12:58.160 --> 13:00.360
The one with ten rolls.
It's a better deal.

13:05.680 --> 13:06.680
The price has gone up?

13:07.200 --> 13:08.520
It seems a bit expensive.

13:21.120 --> 13:23.720
Hi. Do you want cherries?
They just arrived today.

13:23.800 --> 13:25.880
Very fresh. You can have a taste.

13:25.960 --> 13:27.640
Why not take some home for your wife?

13:38.200 --> 13:39.160
Help me taste it.

13:43.760 --> 13:45.160
Your wife is so beautiful.

13:46.880 --> 13:49.080
Sorry, but we're not.

13:49.880 --> 13:51.120
Mine…

13:51.760 --> 13:53.240
Sang Yan's…

13:57.800 --> 13:58.920
Shared…

14:03.560 --> 14:06.800
All right. Do you need to pay separately?

14:06.880 --> 14:08.200
Together, thank you.

14:08.760 --> 14:10.000
I've already separated them.

14:10.080 --> 14:11.440
- If together…
- Give me three bags, please.

14:11.520 --> 14:12.760
Okay.

14:14.880 --> 14:16.320
It won't be easy for the calculation.

14:17.280 --> 14:19.120
I've already separated everything.
Mine, yours, and ours.

14:26.560 --> 14:27.960
We'll calculate it when we are back.

14:38.880 --> 14:40.240
Let me help you carry some.

14:40.920 --> 14:41.840
You hold the umbrella.

14:44.840 --> 14:48.320
- Where's the umbrella?
- I may have left it in the shopping cart.

14:48.400 --> 14:49.280
Wait for me.

15:27.760 --> 15:30.320
Did you forget your umbrella?
Shall I walk you home?

15:41.680 --> 15:43.160
We have an umbrella. You can move aside.

15:44.800 --> 15:46.040
Are you being jealous of me?

15:46.800 --> 15:48.800
You? No.

15:49.920 --> 15:50.760
Hold this.

16:03.400 --> 16:06.040
Shift the umbrella to you a bit.
It's blocking my view.

16:09.240 --> 16:10.120
Shift it more.

16:11.560 --> 16:13.200
Don't you know about your height?

16:15.560 --> 16:17.400
Then, why don't you hold the umbrella?

16:17.480 --> 16:19.360
What are you talking about?
You won't do a little bit of work?

16:29.560 --> 16:30.880
Who was that boy?

16:31.480 --> 16:32.360
I don't know.

16:32.440 --> 16:35.040
He just appeared behind me from nowhere
and asked to walk me home.

16:35.840 --> 16:37.480
He looks a bit familiar to me.

16:37.560 --> 16:40.320
There are a lot of bad people pretending
to be friendly. Don't be silly.

16:45.080 --> 16:45.960
Get in the car.

17:16.680 --> 17:19.720
Do you want to take a hot shower?
You'll catch a cold this way.

17:25.560 --> 17:28.920
His clothes are already wet,
but he's still trying to act tough.

17:37.160 --> 17:38.600
Cold medicine. It's hot. Be careful.

17:42.800 --> 17:43.640
This bag of things is all yours.

17:47.520 --> 17:48.360
These…

17:49.440 --> 17:50.480
We'll use them together.

17:51.120 --> 17:53.560
- But it's hard to calculate.
- It's on me.

19:05.200 --> 19:09.640
MU CHENGYUN, ACTOR
KNOWN FOR WAKING UP TO GHOSTS

19:15.840 --> 19:19.120
What are you doing?
Recommend a horror movie to me

19:19.640 --> 19:20.680
to help me sleep.

19:29.400 --> 19:31.680
A rising star for horror movies…

20:35.960 --> 20:37.400
Do you have to save power like this?

20:38.000 --> 20:39.400
Isn't it better

20:39.920 --> 20:41.280
to watch a horror movie like this?

20:44.160 --> 20:45.000
Indeed.

20:46.160 --> 20:48.600
It seems that people who are scared
prefer to turn off the lights

20:48.680 --> 20:49.680
to create an atmosphere.

20:50.880 --> 20:51.760
They're just acting tough.

20:53.560 --> 20:56.600
I usually turn off the lights
when I watch horror movies.

21:09.400 --> 21:10.280
Dad!

21:12.240 --> 21:13.920
I miss you so much!

21:16.760 --> 21:19.320
Do I look like your dad?

21:27.040 --> 21:28.720
I've calculated the payment.
I'll transfer it to you now.

21:35.960 --> 21:37.320
WEN YIFAN ¥668.00

21:48.520 --> 21:50.720
Why are you laughing? Is it funny?

21:50.800 --> 21:52.240
I laugh because of the movie.

21:52.840 --> 21:55.240
This movie is probably a low-budget film.

21:55.320 --> 21:57.840
The thing covering
the actors' faces looks like flour.

22:05.240 --> 22:07.480
Didn't you notice
the flour on their faces fell off

22:07.560 --> 22:08.600
in a fight scene?

22:10.920 --> 22:12.960
I don't think the movie will scare anyone.

22:18.840 --> 22:20.720
Haven't you seen this movie?

22:22.080 --> 22:23.040
Have you?

22:25.640 --> 22:27.240
We watched it together in Beiyu.

22:28.840 --> 22:30.120
Do you not remember?

22:31.160 --> 22:33.120
I do remember watching a movie with you.

22:33.200 --> 22:36.520
But… I just can't remember
what we watched.

22:36.600 --> 22:37.440
Then, why are you watching it?

23:06.640 --> 23:07.920
Hey,

23:08.000 --> 23:09.240
why did you pause it?

23:09.320 --> 23:11.360
Finally, here's the atmosphere,
but you are ruining it.

23:12.080 --> 23:13.640
Now you want the atmosphere.

23:16.400 --> 23:17.240
It's really him!

23:17.320 --> 23:18.200
MU CHENGYUN, ACTOR

23:24.560 --> 23:26.960
You can recognize him,
even if he's painted up like this.

23:31.920 --> 23:33.200
Where are you going?

23:33.280 --> 23:34.320
I'm going back to my room.
I'll stop bothering you.

23:34.400 --> 23:36.760
It's just a horror movie.
Do you have to be like this?

23:42.400 --> 23:43.520
Are you scared?

23:57.600 --> 23:58.640
All right, Wen Yifan.

24:12.360 --> 24:13.200
What do you mean?

24:14.440 --> 24:15.280
Just sit down.

24:16.600 --> 24:18.400
I know you're scared too.

24:18.480 --> 24:20.480
Why did he say "too"?

24:20.560 --> 24:21.800
It was he who wanted to watch it.

24:21.880 --> 24:23.040
I'm not scared.

24:48.000 --> 24:49.760
So, at that time,

24:49.840 --> 24:52.840
Sang Yan fell asleep
because he was scared of ghosts.

25:04.360 --> 25:07.280
I'm afraid… I might get scared later.

25:16.200 --> 25:17.200
It's fine.

25:18.040 --> 25:18.920
I'm here.

25:23.840 --> 25:24.680
Why are you laughing?

25:32.320 --> 25:33.640
You've laughed several times already.

25:35.880 --> 25:37.080
It's not that funny, is it?

25:59.120 --> 26:00.320
Good morning.

26:00.400 --> 26:02.520
You are up early. You didn't sleep well?

26:03.360 --> 26:04.560
It was okay.

26:04.640 --> 26:07.400
Where are you going
dressed so formally in the early morning?

26:08.680 --> 26:10.560
I have a job interview.

26:12.440 --> 26:13.720
You are looking for a job?

26:13.800 --> 26:15.560
The jobs are looking for me.

26:15.640 --> 26:17.480
Many companies want me so badly.

26:17.560 --> 26:19.480
I picked one that I like
and will see it today.

26:20.160 --> 26:22.200
- How about Overtime?
- It's my bywork.

26:25.920 --> 26:28.160
- Good luck.
- Are you going out?

26:29.160 --> 26:30.480
I have an appointment.

26:35.640 --> 26:37.800
- You scored first in the written exam.
- Yes.

26:38.360 --> 26:39.200
Do you play games?

26:40.400 --> 26:41.240
Yes.

26:42.080 --> 26:43.600
Can you tell me more about it?

26:44.360 --> 26:46.680
Usually, I play MMO games.

26:46.760 --> 26:51.160
All kinds of them,
such as SLG, ACT and RPG.

26:51.880 --> 26:54.040
But I play turn-based games most.

26:54.120 --> 26:57.720
Then, could you tell me
which algorithm is the best

26:57.800 --> 26:59.520
when designing combat values
for turn-based games?

27:00.120 --> 27:01.040
Probably a subtraction formula.

27:01.840 --> 27:04.040
Turn-based combat may look simple,

27:04.720 --> 27:07.240
but every move
is a battle of wits between players.

27:07.320 --> 27:09.000
The subtraction formula
is simple and easy to understand.

27:09.080 --> 27:11.160
It reflects changes in values clearly

27:11.240 --> 27:13.240
and demonstrates strategic value.

27:13.880 --> 27:15.720
This is something
the division formula lacks.

27:16.920 --> 27:19.280
So, what expectations do you have
for our company?

27:19.880 --> 27:20.760
I have none.

27:21.400 --> 27:23.040
- What about the salary?
- It's written on it.

27:24.920 --> 27:26.320
I'll ask you directly.

27:26.880 --> 27:29.600
Why did you apply to work in our company?

27:30.680 --> 27:33.840
You need to work hard
since your look isn't an advantage.

27:34.640 --> 27:37.360
Don't just stay at home
like an unemployed man every day.

27:38.280 --> 27:40.680
They asked you about your work today.

27:44.240 --> 27:47.680
- To find a job.
- To find a job?

27:48.680 --> 27:50.440
Okay. The last question.

27:51.480 --> 27:52.600
What do you think

27:53.240 --> 27:55.640
is the most important thing
to design a game?

27:59.360 --> 28:02.200
What would be the reason for you
to start playing games?

28:04.840 --> 28:05.680
Probably loneliness.

28:07.400 --> 28:08.600
Everyone will feel lonely.

28:10.560 --> 28:12.240
They want companionship in games.

28:17.240 --> 28:18.360
It's okay if you want to meet.

28:18.440 --> 28:20.040
But why did you choose
to meet around my place?

28:22.400 --> 28:23.280
Well, I just think

28:23.360 --> 28:26.040
you don't have to go too far to be here
after you finish work.

28:26.120 --> 28:28.400
Then you can go home and rest
after we finish our discussion here.

28:29.040 --> 28:32.040
You have got the wrong idea.
How can I finish work that early?

28:32.120 --> 28:34.160
I almost work around the clock.

28:34.680 --> 28:36.640
Besides, I'm not your girlfriend.

28:36.720 --> 28:37.640
You don't have to be so considerate.

28:39.880 --> 28:42.160
Maybe I felt this a nice place

28:42.240 --> 28:44.600
when I sent you home last time.
We can hang out a bit.

28:44.680 --> 28:45.800
So…

28:45.880 --> 28:48.080
I really don't know
what a man like you has in mind.

28:48.160 --> 28:49.000
What kind of man I am?

28:49.080 --> 28:50.760
Anyway, we are a different kind of people.

28:50.840 --> 28:52.240
What's the difference?

28:52.320 --> 28:53.720
What should I say
if my grandparents ask about you,

28:53.800 --> 28:55.080
since you don't take my orders anymore?

28:55.160 --> 28:56.720
It's true I'm not taking
your orders anymore.

28:56.800 --> 28:58.560
But I can still help you as a friend.

29:04.360 --> 29:05.800
Thank you for calling me a friend.

29:06.640 --> 29:07.480
I almost forgot.

29:11.760 --> 29:12.680
This is for you.

29:13.880 --> 29:16.160
- What's this?
- Look at your hands.

29:18.680 --> 29:20.720
They'll rot
if you don't put on hand cream.

29:21.920 --> 29:23.920
Take it. Take it.

29:30.280 --> 29:31.160
I have a new order.

29:31.840 --> 29:33.360
I have to leave now.
Don't forget to apply hand cream.

30:10.080 --> 30:12.320
Mrs. Su? What are you doing here?

30:12.400 --> 30:13.360
Hi.

30:15.680 --> 30:16.720
It was you who placed the order?

30:17.680 --> 30:20.160
Just tell me directly
if there's anything you need help with.

30:20.240 --> 30:21.400
No need to place an order.

30:21.480 --> 30:24.600
But you're doing business.
You don't have to be polite to me.

30:26.520 --> 30:30.520
But all you added
for the order was "Support."

30:31.040 --> 30:31.880
What should I do?

30:39.240 --> 30:41.400
- Where are we going?
- Step back a little.

30:41.480 --> 30:42.720
So, what kind of order is it today?

30:42.800 --> 30:44.240
"Caught in the act" order.

30:44.840 --> 30:47.240
Target, Su Haoan's grandfather.

30:48.400 --> 30:50.920
- What does it mean?
- There's no time to explain it to you.

30:51.600 --> 30:53.720
Just do what I tell you later.

30:54.760 --> 30:55.600
Let's go.

30:56.200 --> 30:57.640
Madam.

30:57.720 --> 30:59.440
May I ask who the leader is?

30:59.520 --> 31:01.320
Fang! Someone wants to see you.

31:01.400 --> 31:03.400
- Okay.
- Fang.

31:03.480 --> 31:04.320
What's up?

31:04.400 --> 31:07.160
Well, can we sign up to join you?

31:07.240 --> 31:08.080
You?

31:08.880 --> 31:11.560
Don't you see we are all old people?

31:11.640 --> 31:13.400
This is a government welfare arrangement.

31:13.480 --> 31:15.720
What are you young girls
doing here with us?

31:16.520 --> 31:17.480
Fang!

31:18.120 --> 31:19.840
- We've been waiting for you.
- Okay, just a moment.

31:19.920 --> 31:20.920
- Here I am.
- Let's go.

31:21.000 --> 31:23.320
Mr. Su! Mr. Su!

31:23.400 --> 31:25.320
Lin, what brings you here?

31:26.080 --> 31:27.560
- Lin.
- You two know each other?

31:28.160 --> 31:29.440
My granddaughter-in-law.

31:29.520 --> 31:32.280
Mr. Su, we haven't married yet.

31:32.360 --> 31:34.720
Can we go together then?
Let's just say we're dancing with you.

31:35.440 --> 31:37.280
Oh, here. My friend will join us too.

31:37.360 --> 31:38.800
- I…
- Together.

31:39.400 --> 31:40.480
What do you think?

31:41.000 --> 31:42.320
- It's okay.
- That's great!

31:42.400 --> 31:43.760
Thank you, Fang.

31:43.840 --> 31:46.240
You must be a good dancer, Mr. Su.

31:46.320 --> 31:49.680
- He dances really well.
- That's awesome.

31:54.600 --> 31:56.120
I'm sorry, Mr. Su. I'm sorry.

31:56.200 --> 31:57.480
Does it hurt, Mr. Su?

31:57.560 --> 32:00.240
Lin, your sense of dance rhythm

32:00.320 --> 32:02.240
needs some improvement.

32:02.320 --> 32:04.880
How about this?
You practice over there first.

32:04.960 --> 32:06.680
We'll dance together
after your practice, okay?

32:06.760 --> 32:08.880
- I'm really sorry, Mr. Su.
- It's okay.

32:08.960 --> 32:11.440
- Dian.
- I…

32:13.080 --> 32:15.120
- Hello, Mr. Su. I'm Qiao,
- You'll learn it real quick.

32:15.200 --> 32:16.480
Lin's friend.

32:16.560 --> 32:17.600
Please teach me.

32:18.200 --> 32:19.200
You?

32:20.640 --> 32:22.520
Okay. Come on.

32:35.840 --> 32:36.720
Very good.

32:37.320 --> 32:38.800
You learned it so quickly.

32:39.480 --> 32:40.680
Thank you, Fang.

32:42.520 --> 32:43.800
Listen to me, everyone.

32:43.880 --> 32:46.000
Let's take a break now. Drink some water.

32:46.080 --> 32:47.120
You've worked hard.

32:47.920 --> 32:49.200
Fang,

32:49.280 --> 32:50.920
why didn't your husband
come to dance with you?

32:51.000 --> 32:52.200
My husband?

32:52.880 --> 32:53.920
He passed away a long time ago.

32:57.920 --> 32:59.000
Young lady…

32:59.960 --> 33:02.720
You are Mr. Su's granddaughter-in-law?

33:03.360 --> 33:04.400
- Yes.
- I heard

33:04.480 --> 33:06.240
that his wife left with someone else.

33:06.320 --> 33:08.120
That's not true.

33:08.840 --> 33:12.440
Mr. Su, who usually dances with you?

33:12.960 --> 33:15.280
It depends. This one today.

33:15.360 --> 33:16.520
That one tomorrow.

33:17.920 --> 33:18.840
I see.

33:20.040 --> 33:22.760
- Do you have a boyfriend?
- Not yet.

33:23.520 --> 33:26.520
Shall I ask my grandson
to introduce someone to you?

33:26.600 --> 33:28.840
He has a friend who's still single.

33:28.920 --> 33:31.120
And he keeps bothering
my grandson all day long.

33:31.200 --> 33:33.120
The two of them run a bar together.

33:36.240 --> 33:39.000
No, thanks.
There's already someone I like.

33:39.640 --> 33:40.800
Someone you like?

33:41.480 --> 33:44.680
Then you should make the move
and pursue your own happiness.

33:45.800 --> 33:48.360
Otherwise, you'll regret it

33:49.520 --> 33:50.760
when you come to my age.

33:51.520 --> 33:53.160
You have regrets too, Mr. Su?

33:56.160 --> 33:57.320
Come on.

33:57.400 --> 33:59.080
‪Yeah, hurry up and go!

33:59.160 --> 34:01.000
- Thank you, Mr. Su.
- Hurry up and go!

34:01.880 --> 34:02.840
Mr. Su.

34:02.920 --> 34:04.840
I didn't expect you to learn so fast.

34:04.920 --> 34:05.880
Mr. Su,

34:05.960 --> 34:08.400
you are such a good dancer.
I have to dance with you someday.

34:11.080 --> 34:12.360
Look,

34:12.440 --> 34:13.800
is she the lady in red?

34:15.120 --> 34:17.080
Which one do you mean with so many in red?

34:17.159 --> 34:18.080
Fang!

34:18.639 --> 34:20.760
She's putting her hands on him!

34:23.080 --> 34:24.960
It can't be that easy to guess.

34:26.280 --> 34:28.520
Can there be more than one?

34:30.239 --> 34:32.360
Today, I am inviting you to have some tea.

34:33.840 --> 34:35.719
Mr. Su, can we join you?

34:35.800 --> 34:37.960
Of course. Come on!

34:44.480 --> 34:46.760
Sang Yan!

34:53.960 --> 34:56.120
Just call me if you need any help

34:56.199 --> 34:57.880
with the company. I'll have your back.

35:04.320 --> 35:06.080
- What?
- Give me your hand.

35:07.320 --> 35:10.120
You are hired.
We're colleagues from now on, bro.

35:10.200 --> 35:12.160
Why not move closer to the company?
We can play games together after work.

35:13.160 --> 35:14.800
Who wants to play with you?
You are a bad player.

35:17.720 --> 35:19.760
I think you're used to living
with Wen Yifan

35:19.840 --> 35:21.000
and don't want to leave her.

35:21.640 --> 35:24.400
Let's have dinner together tonight
for a celebration.

35:25.000 --> 35:26.840
I'll invite Zhong Siqiao to join us.

35:32.240 --> 35:34.360
Qiao, let's have dinner together tonight.

35:36.240 --> 35:37.440
Invite Wen Yifan to join us too.

35:39.760 --> 35:41.040
I'll send you the address.

35:42.320 --> 35:43.440
Sang Yan! You're not going?

35:44.360 --> 35:45.360
Sang Yan!

35:51.320 --> 35:54.000
- Have some tea.
- Thank you.

35:54.080 --> 35:55.440
Make yourselves at home. Just eat.

35:55.520 --> 35:56.400
It's so rich.

35:56.480 --> 35:57.400
- It smells so good.
- Eat that.

35:57.480 --> 35:59.440
- I really want to eat it.
- Just make yourselves at home.

35:59.520 --> 36:00.600
- Feel free to eat.
- Okay.

36:04.680 --> 36:06.040
Let me tell you,

36:06.120 --> 36:08.640
the pineapple buns here
are especially authentic.

36:09.320 --> 36:11.960
They're exactly the same
as the ones I had in Hong Kong.

36:12.040 --> 36:13.000
Look,

36:13.080 --> 36:15.120
the crust is very flaky.

36:15.200 --> 36:16.960
With this butter,

36:17.040 --> 36:19.440
it can be called the world's delicacy.

36:20.120 --> 36:22.600
- What Mr. Su recommends must be delicious.
- It's good. Here.

36:22.680 --> 36:26.120
Mr. Su, eating too much butter
isn't good for your health.

36:26.920 --> 36:29.240
How about I get you
something else instead of this?

36:30.120 --> 36:32.360
Young lady, people our age

36:32.440 --> 36:34.400
should eat whatever they want

36:34.480 --> 36:36.520
and date whoever they like.

36:36.600 --> 36:39.160
We want to live freely,
like you young people.

36:39.240 --> 36:40.560
That's what matters. Don't you think so?

36:40.640 --> 36:43.040
- Exactly.
- Mr. Su,

36:43.120 --> 36:45.240
- do you think I'm right?
- This isn't good for your health.

36:45.320 --> 36:46.680
I'll order something else for you.

36:46.760 --> 36:48.600
Here, look at this delicious dish.

36:48.680 --> 36:49.880
- You have to eat this.
- Come on.

36:49.960 --> 36:52.000
It's full of nutrition.

36:52.560 --> 36:54.000
- With a bite of the dish.
- Here.

36:54.080 --> 36:55.120
- With a sip of tea.
- Here's the char siu bao.

36:55.200 --> 36:58.280
- This is good too.
- Thank you.

36:58.360 --> 36:59.280
Thank you.

36:59.360 --> 37:01.040
- Eat this, Mr. Su.
- Come on.

37:05.160 --> 37:06.680
- This is for you.
- Thank you, Mr. Su.

37:06.760 --> 37:07.960
- Don't be too polite. Let's eat.
- Come on.

37:08.040 --> 37:09.720
I got one for you too.

37:10.640 --> 37:11.880
We're going to the bathroom.

37:12.600 --> 37:15.640
- And this…
- Shrimp dumpling.

37:15.720 --> 37:17.280
Yes!

37:17.360 --> 37:18.200
Which one?

37:18.760 --> 37:19.640
Over there.

37:21.640 --> 37:23.240
Look at that one next to your grandfather.

37:23.320 --> 37:25.080
She was serving dishes
to your grandfather.

37:26.120 --> 37:27.040
Well,

37:27.760 --> 37:30.520
Grandma is more beautiful.
Grandpa may not really like her.

37:30.600 --> 37:31.960
Love isn't just about looks.

37:32.040 --> 37:34.960
I'm being honest. Grandma
is indeed more beautiful than her.

37:35.040 --> 37:36.840
Men only care about looks.

37:43.800 --> 37:46.360
YU DA SHI

37:46.440 --> 37:50.320
HOT POT

37:50.400 --> 37:52.400
Thank you for today.

37:52.480 --> 37:54.080
You got up early for my grandpa's issue.

37:54.160 --> 37:56.400
You treat us to dinner just for this?

37:56.480 --> 37:57.360
In the beginning,

37:57.440 --> 38:00.160
I wanted to celebrate Sang Yan
for getting a new job.

38:00.240 --> 38:01.320
But he wouldn't come.

38:04.040 --> 38:07.400
Sang Yan's new job is settled?

38:08.760 --> 38:10.760
Don't worry. I'll have his back

38:11.480 --> 38:12.840
in the company.

38:13.680 --> 38:15.080
He is really tough to deal with.

38:15.160 --> 38:17.320
He looks tough.
Everything about him is tough.

38:17.400 --> 38:18.600
What's wrong with him?

38:19.920 --> 38:21.480
Talking bad about me when I'm not around?

38:22.280 --> 38:23.480
Bro! Why are you here?

38:24.160 --> 38:26.120
Surprising me? Good.

38:28.200 --> 38:30.120
Our hero is here. Come on.

38:30.200 --> 38:31.440
Let's have a drink.

38:31.520 --> 38:33.640
Toast to Sang Yan for joining my company.

38:33.720 --> 38:34.920
Congratulations.

38:39.000 --> 38:41.760
But, Sang Yan,
why did you suddenly want a job?

38:41.840 --> 38:42.920
After he graduated,

38:43.000 --> 38:44.560
he went straight
to a big company in Nanwu.

38:44.640 --> 38:47.520
But who knows what got into him?
He suddenly quit.

38:47.600 --> 38:49.240
Stop talking too much. Drink it.

38:51.520 --> 38:52.600
Okay.

38:53.960 --> 38:56.080
Yifan, thank you for today.

38:56.160 --> 38:57.320
Thank you.

38:57.400 --> 38:59.720
You are welcome.
I'm having an off day anyway.

38:59.800 --> 39:01.000
Consider it spending time with Qiao.

39:02.960 --> 39:05.000
What do you think first love even means?

39:06.000 --> 39:07.280
What's the meaning
of being together for decades?

39:07.920 --> 39:11.320
I really feel bad for my grandma.
Grandpa was her first love.

39:11.960 --> 39:13.360
He's already at an old age

39:13.440 --> 39:15.920
but is still messing around
with those dance teachers.

39:16.000 --> 39:17.440
He's really troublesome.

39:23.200 --> 39:25.000
I will definitely ask her why
she would ruin another woman's family

39:25.080 --> 39:26.320
when I find her out!

39:26.400 --> 39:27.880
That's not what I meant.

39:28.680 --> 39:30.360
I want to ask you

39:30.440 --> 39:32.560
to help me find out if she's reliable.

39:34.000 --> 39:34.880
Is she reliable?

39:36.680 --> 39:39.080
If she is reliable

39:39.840 --> 39:42.280
and they truly love each other,

39:42.360 --> 39:44.200
I will support them.

39:45.320 --> 39:48.640
Mrs. Su, you are too good to her.

39:50.920 --> 39:52.720
Do you think

39:52.800 --> 39:56.280
it's good love
when neither of them is happy

39:57.040 --> 39:58.320
being together?

40:00.120 --> 40:02.120
Forcing it won't bring happiness.

40:02.960 --> 40:05.840
What if he happens to meet the one

40:05.920 --> 40:08.920
he feels is the most important in life?

40:09.000 --> 40:10.120
What should we do?

40:12.960 --> 40:15.240
Mrs. Su, you'd better

40:15.320 --> 40:17.440
have a good talk with Mr. Su first.

40:17.520 --> 40:19.080
What should we talk about?

40:19.160 --> 40:21.840
Lately, he forgets everything I tell him.

40:21.920 --> 40:24.280
He doesn't even remember my birthday.

40:24.360 --> 40:26.840
His mind is no longer on me.

40:26.920 --> 40:29.200
Why should I hold on to him?

40:35.800 --> 40:38.520
It seems that, for men,
first love is nothing to them.

40:40.120 --> 40:42.680
Maybe only girls care more
about their first love.

40:45.680 --> 40:47.000
Not necessarily.

40:47.080 --> 40:50.200
The place of first love is irreplaceable.

40:53.600 --> 40:55.160
You're talking
as if you really understand.

40:57.800 --> 41:00.360
Talk less. Cheers!

41:27.640 --> 41:31.360
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

45:09.720 --> 45:10.800
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:10.880 --> 45:11.880
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
